E2FAAU.original: ~z~There a driving range round here, ain't there? That's what rich people do, ain't it?
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~附近有个高尔夫练习场对吧？这就是有钱人的运动吧？

E2FAAU.original: ~z~You fucking joking. You the rich bitch. Ain't giving you shit for free.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~你他妈搞笑呢。你这么有钱，别想白嫖老子。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~Luis Lopez. What's up?
E2FA_AEA
E2FA_AYA
~z~If you going down, you may as well have this with you.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~还有需要的话，最好再买个这个。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~I had all your money and leisure time, L. I'd definitely beat you.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~我要是像你这样有钱又有闲的话，L，你绝逼赢不了。

E2FAAU.original: E2FA_ADA
~z~Coño, monstruo. I thought you were 24/7, bro. Sorry.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~妈的，猛男。我还以为你是007，兄弟。打扰了。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~I guess you don't got the hustlers touch, double L.
E2FA_IA
~z~I ain't in the mood for this?
E2FA_BZA
~z~This will get your dick hard.
~z~We close to them fine titties at the Triangle.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~我们去三角俱乐部看大咪咪吧。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~Mando, sorry loco. But I can't hang with you no more. Tell H.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~Mando，不好意思啊。但我没法陪你们出去了。跟H说下吧。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~Later on, L.
~z~Sounds like a plan, A. Hang out for a minute and I'll be by.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~这主意不错，A。你先溜达会儿，我马上过来。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~It's money outta my pocket if I give you that for free.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~这都白送给你就是我撒币了。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~I'm trying to run a business. Shit.
~z~Oye, Mando, I need some hardware. You available?
~z~Coño, that's a shame. Another time.
E2FA_AMA
~z~This might help when the shit hits.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~出事的时候这个能派上用场。

E2FAAU.original: E2FA_KA
~z~Northwood's son, Downtown's bitch. What's happening?
~z~Shit. Sorry, pa.
~z~I'm doing you a favor. You forget that?
~z~Tasty shit, no?
~z~I bet you don't pull out half way when you looking after the boss, L.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~保护老板的时候你一定不会中途跑路吧，L。

E2FAAU.original: E2FA_OA
~z~I like it.
~z~You're there, bro. Sorry to do this, but I got to cancel on our plans. We'll do it another time.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~是你吗，兄弟。很不好意思，但我们的计划得取消了。咱们改天再约吧。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~I don't know about you, but I could do with some fried Chicken.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~我想去吃顿炸鸡，不知道你意下如何。

E2FAAU.original: E2FA_WA
~z~What you doing, bro?
~z~Okay, pues. Tell H I called.
E2FA_TA
~z~I guess we evenly matched. Remember that next time you want to condescend.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~下次又想装逼的时候，你记好了，咱们的水平可是不相上下的。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~That's how you do it. A working man's game.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~打工仔的游戏，打工仔才能赢。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~We done darts, now let's go shoot some fuckers.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~飞镖投完了，现在该来真刀真枪的了。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~Why you fucking with me?
~z~If you need it, you need it. I don't want my boy getting hurt.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~你说需要，那就是有必要。我可不想我的人受伤。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~Coño, mano. Okay, bro. Call me soon.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~妈的，就这样吧，兄弟。以后再约。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~You too busy to hang with the family, bro? Let's you and me and Rique go out.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~你有空陪家人们出去玩吗，兄弟？你、我，还有Rique一起出去吧。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~Nos vemos, loco. Say hi to H for me.
E2FA_ALA
~z~Henrique's had one of his fits, bro. You know, the ones you ain't had to deal with since you left? It's gonna have to be another time.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~Henrique有事要忙，兄弟。你懂的，你走了以后他就接过了你的重担。看来得改天再约了。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~This just the thing.
E2FA_AFA
E2FA_ABA
~z~Everything gets better when you drunk.
~z~You want me to turn one them pieces on you, bro. I will.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~你是想让我拿你试枪是吧，兄弟。我会的。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~He got hisself in a fight, has he? I'll come by.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~他又惹上事了，不是吗？我会过来的。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~Downtown. It's your boy from the Heights.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~城里人，我是你在高地的哥们。

E2FAAU.original: E2FA_BVA
~z~This is Armando's personal, non business related, totally one hundred percent legitimate cell phone. Leave a message.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~这是Armando私人的、百分百合法的非工作手机号。请留言。

E2FAAU.original: E2FA_AUA
~z~Thanks, A. Shit is so fucked up right now that might be useful. I'll call you.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~谢了，A。现在世道不太平，这会很有用的。有需要了我就找你。

E2FAAU.original: E2FA_BUA
~z~Yo, man. You left H. Shit.
~z~Check it out.
~z~And then he was gone.
~z~You know what? Stay Downtown. We don't want you up here. Conyo.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~送你句话，城里待着吧你。我们不需要你了。妈的。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~He don't even got the time to finish a dart game.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~他甚至都没空玩完一把飞镖。

E2FAAU.original: E2FA_RA
~z~Yo, L. If you ever need some weaponry gimme a call. I can come by in my van and sell you shit at cost.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~哟，L。以后需要武器了就给我打个电话。我可以开车过来，按成本价卖给你。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~Rique ain't gonna believe I got a call from you, bro. He was sure you were dead or something. Pick us up in the next two hours.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~Rique肯定不相信我接到了你的电话，兄弟。他以为你已经死了。两小时内来接我们吧。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~I'm splitting.
E2FA_BFA
~z~Fuck, bro. We left H. I hope he alright.
E2FAAU.translated: ~z~操，兄弟。咱把H落下了。希望他没事。

E2FAAU.original: ~z~What were we doing in there.
~z~Let's just go get us a drink.
